    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is an investment-grade E46 M3, a definitive analog masterpiece. This specimen features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine, characterized by its six individual throttle bodies and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is impeccable, with a documented subframe reinforcement and a recently overhauled VANOS system to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior retains a deep factory luster with no orange peel or pitting. This is a turn-key, collector-spec vehicle for the driver who demands mechanical perfection and surgical handling.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
