    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece: a time-capsule specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its deep, mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery retains its factory scent and supple texture, showing zero signs of wear on the bolsters or controls. Every mechanical component has been serviced ahead of schedule using only OEM parts, ensuring a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive service binder. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
